data.name: laySubHangmog.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DECODE(B.HANGMOG_CODE,B.SOURCE_GUMSA,'',' ') || C.GUMSA_NAME GUMSA_NAME, B.RESULT_DATE RESULT_DATE, B.CPL_RESULT CPL_RESULT FROM CPL0101 C, CPL3020 B, CPL2010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND B.CONFIRM_DATE IS NOT NULL AND B.FKCPL2010 = A.PKCPL2010 AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = B.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.SPECIMEN_CODE = B.SPECIMEN_CODE AND C.EMERGENCY = B.EMERGENCY ORDER BY B.RESULT_DATE DESC

data.name: grdOrderList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.ORDER_DATE AS ORDER_DATE --, A.IN_OUT_GUBUN AS IN_OUT_GUBUN , CASE WHEN A.IN_OUT_GUBUN ='O' THEN '外' WHEN A.IN_OUT_GUBUN ='I' THEN '入' END IN_OUT_GUBUN , DECODE(A.IN_OUT_GUBUN,'O', A.GWA, FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_GWA(A.FKOCS2003)) AS GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.ORDER_DATE) AS GWA_NAME , DECODE(A.IN_OUT_GUBUN,'O', A.DOCTOR, FN_OCS_LOAD_ORDER_DOCTOR(A.FKOCS2003)) AS DOCTOR , FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) AS DOCTOR_NAME FROM CPL2010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.ORDER_DATE IS NOT NULL AND A.JUBSU_DATE IS NOT NULL AND ( ( A.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.FKOCS1003 NOT IN (SELECT X.FKOCS1003 FROM CPL2010 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND X.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND X.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'I' AND X.FKOCS1003 IS NOT NULL ) ) OR ( A.IN_OUT_GUBUN <> 'O' ) ) ORDER BY A.ORDER_DATE DESC

data.name: layMakeTabPage.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT '%' , '全体' FROM SYS.DUAL UNION ALL SELECT A.CODE , A.CODE_NAME FROM V_CPL_DATA_CODE A -- CPL0109 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.CODE_TYPE = '01' AND A.START_DATE <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) AND A.END_DATE_REAL >= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ORDER BY 1
